From 20a6ed80cf06d91aa9d10653da1b96e40fce20bf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Tomasz=20Paku=C5=82a?= <tomasz.pakula.oficjalny@gmail.com>
